---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";


---

<Layout title="About Us | My Blog" description="Learn more about our mission, vision, and values.">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class=" max-w-screen-md mx-auto py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-indigo-700 mb-4">About Us</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-indigo-900 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Discover our story, our mission, and how we aim to bring you high-quality content across multiple categories. Our blog is designed to educate, inspire, and keep you informed.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section class="py-16 max-w-screen-md mx-auto">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
        My Blog started with a vision to make learning accessible and engaging for everyone. Over the years, we have explored diverse topics ranging from technology, coding tutorials, lifestyle, and productivity. Our aim is to combine **knowledge with practical insights**.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We believe that information should be **clear, organized, and actionable**. Each post is carefully researched and presented in a way that is easy to digest for readers of all levels.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision Section -->
  <section class="py-16 max-w-screen-md mx-auto">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-900 mb-6">Mission & Vision</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">
            To provide high-quality, curated content that empowers readers to learn, explore, and grow. We aim to make our blog a **trusted resource** for knowledge seekers across multiple domains.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Vision</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">
            To create a platform where information, learning, and inspiration meet. We envision a blog that **not only informs but also motivates action**, enabling readers to achieve their personal and professional goals.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Get in Touch</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Have questions, feedback, or collaboration ideas? Visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">Contact page</a> to reach us.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-indigo-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-800 transition">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
